 Peter Cat Recording Co. 分享丰富多彩的单曲“People Never Change”并“宣布新专辑“BETA” https://www.nme.com/news/music/peter-cat-recording-co-share-colourful-single-people-never-change-announce-new-album-beta-3759816?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=彼得猫录音共同分享色彩缤纷的单身人士永不改变宣布新专辑测试版Hollie GeraghtyMon, 27 May 2024 12:50:57 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndieJazz https://www.nme.com/?p=3759816 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/peter-cat-recording-co-2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="彼得猫唱片公司" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/peter-cat-recording-co-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/peter-cat-recording-co-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/peter-cat-recording-co-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/peter-cat-recording-co-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/peter-cat-recording-co-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/peter-cat-recording-co-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该乐队将他们的新专辑描述为“一本讲述 50 年前未来故事的合集，旨在理解我们唯一的家园——地球上的现在”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/peter-cat-recording-co-share-colourful-single-people-never-change-announce-new-album-beta-3759816">Peter Cat Recording Co. 分享色彩丰富的单曲“People Never Change”并宣布新专辑“BETA”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/peter-cat-recording-co-2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="彼得猫唱片公司" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/peter-cat-recording-co-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/peter-cat-recording-co-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/peter-cat-recording-co-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/peter-cat-recording-co-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/peter-cat-recording-co-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/peter-cat-recording-co-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Peter Cat Recording Co. 推出了一首充满活力的新单曲“People Never Change”，并宣布了他们的下一张专辑“BETA”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/peter-cat-recording-2387812">来认识一下 Peter Cat Recording Co.，这是一家新德里剧团，他们创作了一首不容错过的大型乐队歌曲</a></strong></li></ul><p>这支印度乐队的新单曲是他们即将发行的唱片的主打单曲，该唱片在印地语中是“孩子”的爱称。</p><p>这支跨流派的乐队本月在 Instagram 上宣布了他们“时髦”的新单曲和即将发行的专辑的到来，他们说这张专辑是在三大洲录制的，并且“一路上（恰如其分地）经历了无尽的变化。</p><p> 《BETA》将于 8 月 9 日通过 Muddy Water 发行，随后将在美国、英国、欧洲和印度进行 77 场大型巡演，其中包括为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/khruangbin">Khruangbin</a>提供支持的巡演。</p><p>请听下面的“人永远不会改变”。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="人永远不会改变" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/PVgG5OCWmNE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>新专辑旨在捕捉乐队自结婚生子以来个人的演变。</p><p>乐队在一份新闻稿中表示：“BETA 是一本讲述 50 年前关于未来的故事的合集，旨在理解我们唯一的家园——地球上的现在。”</p><p> 《BETA》只是该项目可能选择的五张专辑之一。他们写下了所有五个，把它们放在帽子里，然后让鼓手卡兰·辛格六个月大的儿子伸手去挑选。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C6wDHP2yOZN/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: